306
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:36,240
No.

307
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:37,790
Auntie, please sit.

308
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:39,790
Well.

309
00:12:42,270 --> 00:12:44,600
