critical illness for you.

310
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:46,320
Okay.

311
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:46,670
Okay.

312
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,030
We'll

313
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,360
