326
00:13:33,270 --> 00:13:34,480
I've already spoken to Chunlu.

327
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,720
But judging from the procedures,

328
00:13:38,270 --> 00:13:39,750
she did nothing wrong.

329
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,240
This matter,

330
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,390
I'm afraid there's no other way.

331
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:49,550
If there's nothing else, I'm off.

332
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:50,720
Wait.

333
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,120
