346
00:14:32,630 --> 00:14:33,670
Serves you right.

347
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:34,750
Great!

348
00:14:59,260 --> 00:15:00,690
[Xue Xiaozhou]

349
00:15:24,550 --> 00:15:27,750
Ya, I'm downstairs at your dorm.

350
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:31,030
Baodan misses you.

351
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,720
It says it wants to see you.

352
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:35,360
Will you come down to meet it?

353
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,240
If you don't come down,

354
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,440
