355
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,720
Which floor is your dorm on?

356
00:15:46,790 --> 00:15:47,630
Which room is yours?

357
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:48,840
I—I'm right downstairs.

358
00:15:55,150 --> 00:15:56,390
Ya, reply my message.

359
00:15:56,390 --> 00:15:56,910
You... you...

360
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:58,150
Just reply.

361
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,080
