363
00:16:00,510 --> 00:16:02,000
You—you're definitely awake, right?

364
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:03,700
[Xue Xiaozhou]

365
00:16:58,870 --> 00:17:00,080
Hey, Manli.

366
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:01,630
Hey, Ya.

367
00:17:02,550 --> 00:17:03,600
Can you talk some sense

368
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:05,960
