369
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:07,440
What's wrong?

370
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:13,110
Ya, I'm still here.

371
00:17:13,110 --> 00:17:14,110
I'm still downstairs.

372
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:15,590
Just come down

373
00:17:16,310 --> 00:17:17,510
to see Baodan.

374
00:17:17,590 --> 00:17:18,550
One meeting and I'll leave.

375
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:33,440
What are you doing?

376
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:36,030
Come back with me, let's go.

377
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:38,070
Baodan wants to see Ya.

378
00:17:38,310 --> 00:17:40,030
