384
00:17:51,590 --> 00:17:53,110
Be careful or Wu Ya might call the cops.

385
00:17:53,270 --> 00:17:54,750
Whatever, I have to see her today!

386
00:18:01,790 --> 00:18:02,680
Which room is hers?

387
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:03,720
I don't know.

388
00:18:04,550 --> 00:18:06,550
You don't know your girlfriend's room?

389
00:18:24,310 --> 00:18:25,480
Ya, which floor are you on?

390
00:18:29,980 --> 00:18:30,340
[Hu Manli]

391
00:18:45,030 --> 00:18:45,640
Ya.

392
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:48,160
It's me, Manli.

393
00:18:49,750 --> 00:18:52,270
If you really want to break up,
give him a reason.

394
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:55,350
Xiaozhou won't understand if you do this.

395
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:57,030
No matter what,

396
00:18:57,680 --> 00:18:59,160
you should talk this through, right?

397
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:04,310
I made everything clear last time.

398
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:07,550
Wait, I'm sorry.

399
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,440
Ya, I...I'm sorry.

400
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,920
Tell me what to change, and I'll change.

401
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:12,480
Ya.

402
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:14,920
Ya.

403
00:19:15,510 --> 00:19:17,790
You two made it through such hard times.

404
00:19:18,350 --> 00:19:20,110
How can you just stop loving him now?

405
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:21,480
What exactly happened?

406
00:19:27,030 --> 00:19:28,640
He's too self-centered, too selfish.

407
00:19:29,790 --> 00:19:31,720
There's no one but himself in his heart.

408
00:19:32,750 --> 00:19:34,030
Maybe I never loved him.

409
00:19:36,590 --> 00:19:38,350
I only loved the idea of him.

410
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:44,720
The real him was never worth my love.

411
00:20:28,550 --> 00:20:29,240
Xiaozhou.

412
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:33,070
He broke up with his girlfriend.

413
00:20:53,830 --> 00:20:54,640
I have an idea.

414
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:56,680
I want to switch to field work.

415
00:20:57,270 --> 00:20:58,720
You want to sell insurance?

416
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:00,510
But you...

417
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:02,240
Are you sure?

418
00:21:09,590 --> 00:21:10,030
Xiaozhou.

419
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:12,110
Relationships between people

420
00:21:12,110 --> 00:21:14,110
require deliberate effort to maintain.

421
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:15,720
Now you're selling insurance,

422
00:21:16,160 --> 00:21:17,350
if you can't learn to please others,

423
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:18,680
why would they sign policies with you?

424
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:21,160
I don't want shady methods to
sell insurance!

425
00:21:22,270 --> 00:21:23,270
This is social etiquette!

426
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:24,400
How is that shady?

427
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:25,590
I know you care about me,

428
00:21:25,590 --> 00:21:27,480
but I want to try my own way.

429
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:29,000
Give me some time, okay?

430
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,720
You can refuse this deal,

431
00:21:38,110 --> 00:21:39,550
