434
00:21:43,550 --> 00:21:45,000
Insuring the mistress next?

435
00:21:45,510 --> 00:21:46,440
Who after that?

436
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:47,400
I dare not imagine.

437
00:21:48,590 --> 00:21:49,960
A three-million-yuan policy.

438
00:21:51,310 --> 00:21:52,920
Think about your mother.

439
00:22:45,590 --> 00:22:46,000
Morning.

440
00:22:46,830 --> 00:22:47,720
Why didn't you call me?

441
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:48,920
Are you okay?

442
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:50,480
I'm fine.

443
00:22:51,110 --> 00:22:52,030
I'll go to the office.

444
00:22:52,030 --> 00:22:53,590
I can drop Daer off at school too.

445
00:22:54,100 --> 00:22:54,750
Ah?

446
00:22:54,750 --> 00:22:55,270
Are you sure?

447
00:22:56,270 --> 00:22:56,720
Of course.

448
00:23:15,350 --> 00:23:16,550
You're sure you're alright?

449
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:18,310
Of course.

450
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:19,310
Don't worry about me.

451
00:23:26,270 --> 00:23:27,240
Last night,

452
00:23:28,110 --> 00:23:29,070
I really thought about it.

453
00:23:30,350 --> 00:23:32,240
These past six months,

454
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:33,480
I've done many things wrong.

455
00:23:34,030 --> 00:23:35,030
I let Ya down.

456
00:23:36,160 --> 00:23:37,240
Ya may seem

457
00:23:37,590 --> 00:23:38,920
cheerful on the surface,

458
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:39,880
but actually...

459
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,070
she takes things to heart.

460
00:23:44,110 --> 00:23:45,270
So what's your plan now?

461
00:23:46,240 --> 00:23:47,880
I'll work hard from now on.

462
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:49,590
Prove it to her with actions.

463
00:23:50,070 --> 00:23:51,200
I won't disappoint her again.

464
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:54,160
Good.

465
00:23:55,110 --> 00:23:55,680
You,

466
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:57,920
just follow my lead, got it?

467
00:23:58,440 --> 00:24:00,400
In six months, we'll get you

468
00:24:00,750 --> 00:24:01,920
a down payment for a small place.

469
00:24:02,590 --> 00:24:03,510
Then you can slap those keys

470
00:24:04,070 --> 00:24:04,960
right in front of her.

471
00:24:05,030 --> 00:24:06,830
Guaranteed to move Ya to tears.

472
00:24:07,590 --> 00:24:08,110
Mom.

473
00:24:08,590 --> 00:24:10,310
Don't make love sound so materialistic, okay?

474
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:11,070
Wrong.

475
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:13,790
A house isn't just material.

476
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:16,640
It also provides spiritual security.

477
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:17,550
Agreed.

478
00:24:18,310 --> 00:24:18,750
Well said.

479
00:24:19,920 --> 00:24:21,240
Learn from Xiaozhou.

480
00:24:21,640 --> 00:24:23,000
He admit him mistakes.

481
00:24:29,500 --> 00:24:31,020
[Chen Fang liked Tang Ling's post]

482
00:24:31,900 --> 00:24:32,380
Hm?

483
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:37,000
They know each other?

484
00:24:48,750 --> 00:24:49,510
You liked my post.

485
00:24:50,440 --> 00:24:50,830
No I didn't.

486
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:52,720
I liked a new property ad.

487
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:55,160
Look yourself - isn't that you?

488
00:24:56,350 --> 00:24:56,830
Cancel it now.

489
00:24:58,790 --> 00:24:59,480
My bad.

490
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:01,880
Be more careful next time.

491
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:04,960
Canceled.

492
00:25:12,740 --> 00:25:13,660
Oh ho?

493
00:25:17,720 --> 00:25:18,160
What's wrong?

494
00:25:20,310 --> 00:25:20,920
Let me ask you.

495
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:23,720
You said back then

496
00:25:24,110 --> 00:25:26,750
Chen Fang asked you to
check my past claims.

497
00:25:28,070 --> 00:25:29,960
You're not bringing up
old grudges again, are you?

498
00:25:30,030 --> 00:25:30,480
Seriously.

499
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:38,160
I always thought I'd offended Chen Fang.

500
00:25:38,160 --> 00:25:39,350
That's why he's messing with me.

501
00:25:39,550 --> 00:25:39,960
Isn't it?

502
00:25:45,790 --> 00:25:46,160
Look.

503
00:25:48,310 --> 00:25:50,160
Chen Fang liked Tang Ling's post.

504
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:52,070
They know each other?

505
00:25:53,830 --> 00:25:55,400
Theoretically,
they shouldn't know each other.

506
00:25:56,830 --> 00:25:59,400
When Tang Ling jumped to TSI,

507
00:25:59,830 --> 00:26:01,110
Chen Fang hadn't joined us yet.

508
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:04,880
But it's normal for people
in the same circle.

509
00:26:05,900 --> 00:26:07,680
Yes.

510
00:26:07,680 --> 00:26:09,720
It's normal for peers to know each other.

511
00:26:10,270 --> 00:26:11,510
Liking each other's posts is normal too.

512
00:26:11,680 --> 00:26:12,270
But look.

513
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:13,680
Now.

514
00:26:14,590 --> 00:26:15,830
Liked, then canceled it.

515
00:26:16,070 --> 00:26:16,960
That's not normal anymore.

516
00:26:20,720 --> 00:26:22,640
Seems they've been involved for a while.

517
00:26:28,310 --> 00:26:29,720
Back when Li Qingqing

518
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:31,750
poached me to TSI as director,

519
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:33,920
Tang Ling must have been scared,

520
00:26:35,400 --> 00:26:36,880
so she teamed up with Chen Fang

521
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:39,240
and used you to take me down.

522
00:26:44,590 --> 00:26:45,400
I see.

523
00:26:47,110 --> 00:26:47,830
That's what happened.

524
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:51,350
They're definitely involved.

525
00:26:51,510 --> 00:26:52,070
What are you doing?

526
00:26:52,510 --> 00:26:53,510
Confront Tang Ling.

527
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:54,680
Sit down.

528
00:26:54,880 --> 00:26:55,480
Sit down.

529
00:26:56,110 --> 00:26:56,750
Sit!

530
00:27:00,790 --> 00:27:01,400
You have no proof.

531
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,920
They'll never admit it.

532
00:27:03,830 --> 00:27:05,270
Besides,
you're Tang Ling's subordinate now.

533
00:27:05,270 --> 00:27:06,680
She can easily make things hard for you.

534
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:09,960
Remember,
just do your job normally at work.

535
00:27:10,590 --> 00:27:11,830
Keep your distance from her.

536
00:27:12,070 --> 00:27:13,790
So you're saying we should let it go?

537
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:16,510
They're in the light while we're hidden.

538
00:27:17,110 --> 00:27:18,750
Revenge is a dish best served cold.

539
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:21,790
You're a heroine, Mom.

540
00:27:22,310 --> 00:27:22,640
No.

541
00:27:23,030 --> 00:27:23,750
You're the queen.

542
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:25,110
I'm the femme fatale.

543
00:27:26,070 --> 00:27:26,680
Listen to me.

544
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:27,720
My goal is crystal clear now.

545
00:27:28,030 --> 00:27:29,000
I want that car.

546
00:27:29,750 --> 00:27:31,030
I said I want that car, hear me?

547
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:32,790
Everything else can wait,
