549
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:44,000
Ling bought it.

550
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,070
Nice.

551
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:46,510
There's enough for everyone.

552
00:27:49,240 --> 00:27:49,550
Xiaozhou.

553
00:27:49,830 --> 00:27:50,440
