557
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,000
How spoiled.

558
00:27:59,750 --> 00:28:00,160
No, thanks.

559
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,310
You guys go ahead.

560
00:28:03,830 --> 00:28:05,030
Refusing her kindness.

561
00:28:10,070 --> 00:28:11,160
Silk-stocking milk tea.

562
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:12,590
Less sugar, less ice.

563
00:28:13,030 --> 00:28:13,480
Is that okay?

564
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:19,830
You have no proof.

565
00:28:19,830 --> 00:28:21,400
They'll never admit it.

566
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:23,680
Besides,
you're now Tang Ling's subordinate.

567
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:25,110
It'd be too easy for her
to mess with you.

568
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:30,160
Thanks.

569
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:33,790
Xiaozhou is our department's lucky star.

570
00:28:34,110 --> 00:28:35,590
Everyone should learn from Xiaozhou.

571
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:38,350
Thanks for the milk tea, Ling.

572
00:28:38,590 --> 00:28:40,590
Learn from Xiaozhou.

573
00:28:44,550 --> 00:28:45,720
Alright, carry on with your work.

574
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:47,030
Let's dig in.

575
00:28:48,550 --> 00:28:48,920
Thank you.

576
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:51,720
Here's yours with 30% sugar.

577
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:53,960
