Professor Ding,
which card for the transfer?

873
00:38:45,110 --> 00:38:45,590
Your bank card.

874
00:38:46,030 --> 00:38:46,480
Here.

875
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:49,800
Here.

876
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:51,280
Thank you.

877
00:38:53,030 --> 00:38:53,480
Okay.

878
00:38:54,710 --> 00:38:55,480
Sorry to trouble you.

879
00:38:55,480 --> 00:38:57,320
Please sign this loan contract first.

880
00:38:58,710 --> 00:38:59,150
What?

881
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:01,110
Loan contract.

882
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:02,760
Simply put, it's an IOU.

883
00:39:05,150 --> 00:39:05,510
Loan...

884
00:39:06,710 --> 00:39:07,590
IOU?

885
00:39:10,030 --> 00:39:10,480
Zhiyuan.

886
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:13,760
This IOU... isn't this...

887
00:39:14,230 --> 00:39:15,230
your partner's money?

888
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:16,280
We're family.

889
00:39:16,630 --> 00:39:17,760
Why need an IOU?

890
00:39:18,510 --> 00:39:19,360
Yes, right.

891
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:20,510
Huang, what's going on?

892
00:39:21,230 --> 00:39:22,110
Don't get it wrong.

893
00:39:22,670 --> 00:39:24,320
This money belongs to the company.

894
00:39:24,630 --> 00:39:25,510
Withdrawing funds

895
00:39:25,510 --> 00:39:27,150
requires financial documentation.

896
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,710
I don't understand your policies.

897
00:39:30,110 --> 00:39:30,800
I only know

898
00:39:31,190 --> 00:39:33,000
we family borrowing some money

899
00:39:33,760 --> 00:39:35,280
don't need an IOU, right?

900
00:39:37,760 --> 00:39:38,400
Sir.

901
00:39:39,230 --> 00:39:40,070
Even though we're family,

902
00:39:40,230 --> 00:39:42,400
it's proper to write an IOU
when borrowing.

903
00:39:43,190 --> 00:39:45,110
Otherwise there's no proof later.

904
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:47,880
Little girl, who do you think you are?

905
00:39:48,480 --> 00:39:49,590
Is this your place to speak?

906
00:39:53,840 --> 00:39:55,030
Uncle, Aunt, don't be angry.

907
00:39:55,480 --> 00:39:58,630
The company has its own regulations.

908
00:39:59,150 --> 00:39:59,510
Well...

909
00:40:00,550 --> 00:40:00,880
How about

910
00:40:01,360 --> 00:40:01,880
you don't sign.

911
00:40:02,190 --> 00:40:02,510
I'll do it.

912
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:05,000
I'll sign it.

913
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:07,590
Professor Ding.

914
00:40:08,280 --> 00:40:08,920
This won't do.

915
00:40:09,190 --> 00:40:10,710
The borrower must sign.

916
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:21,320
Um...

917
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:26,360
Uncle.

918
00:40:27,840 --> 00:40:29,070
Just follow the procedure.

919
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:31,550
Please sign it.

920
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:39,920
Our son's banquet money
isn't settled yet.

921
00:40:42,030 --> 00:40:42,550
Maybe...

922
00:40:46,510 --> 00:40:47,230
We should just sign.

923
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:53,000
Sign it.

924
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:04,710
Don't turn the page.

925
00:41:05,400 --> 00:41:05,670
Wait...

926
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:08,280
What does this clause mean?

927
00:41:09,110 --> 00:41:10,030
Why is there interest?

928
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:12,190
This is even more outrageous.

929
00:41:12,710 --> 00:41:14,280
How come it's due in just half a year?

930
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:16,030
What... what's going on here?

931
00:41:17,070 --> 00:41:17,920
If company funds are

932
00:41:18,320 --> 00:41:19,880
lent to private individuals
for no reason,

933
00:41:20,070 --> 00:41:21,960
with no interest or repayment deadline,

934
00:41:22,550 --> 00:41:23,960
the company audit won't pass it.

935
00:41:27,070 --> 00:41:27,440
Uncle.

936
00:41:27,630 --> 00:41:28,280
Don't worry about it.

937
00:41:28,280 --> 00:41:29,320
Just sign it.

938
00:41:29,400 --> 00:41:29,840
Sign it.

939
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:32,190
Once signed, you must comply.

940
00:41:32,510 --> 00:41:33,550
Let me remind everyone.

941
00:41:34,150 --> 00:41:35,070
Failure to repay on time,

942
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:36,230
the tax bureau will

943
00:41:36,230 --> 00:41:38,480
levy 20% personal income tax

944
00:41:38,840 --> 00:41:40,110
Twenty percent!

945
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:43,280
Ding Zhiyuan!

946
00:41:44,110 --> 00:41:44,440
Uncle.

947
00:41:44,510 --> 00:41:45,800
You... you can't manage this family.

948
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:46,440
I have my dignity!

949
00:41:46,510 --> 00:41:47,190
I'm leaving!

950
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:47,920
No, seriously.

951
00:41:47,920 --> 00:41:49,000
Uncle! You...

952
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:50,030
I...

953
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:51,760
- Auntie! - My card.

954
00:41:52,760 --> 00:41:53,360
Auntie, you...

955
00:41:53,440 --> 00:41:54,030
You're really...

956
00:41:54,030 --> 00:41:54,670
Don't be angry.

957
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:55,400
Really...

958
00:41:56,630 --> 00:41:57,280
Where's Qiu Lisu?

959
00:41:57,550 --> 00:41:58,480
I must see her immediately.

960
00:41:59,510 --> 00:42:00,230
Ms. Qiu is on a business trip.

961
00:42:00,230 --> 00:42:01,070
Which way is downstairs?

962
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:03,000
Which way should we go?

963
00:42:03,070 --> 00:42:03,510
Uncle.

964
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:04,840
Uncle.

965
00:42:05,510 --> 00:42:06,440
That way, go that way.

966
00:42:06,760 --> 00:42:07,960
This way, right this way.

967
00:42:14,320 --> 00:42:15,360
Zhiyuan, tell me.

968
00:42:15,510 --> 00:42:17,190
What was all that farce?

969
00:42:17,590 --> 00:42:19,030
Your uncle just had surgery.

970
00:42:19,150 --> 00:42:20,550
He shouldn't get this worked up.

971
00:42:22,230 --> 00:42:23,590
My partner is away on business.

972
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:25,550
It's all done by her subordinates.

973
00:42:27,190 --> 00:42:27,760
Ding Zhiyuan.

974
00:42:28,320 --> 00:42:29,400
I'm asking you one last time.

975
00:42:30,030 --> 00:42:30,550
That 200K,

976
00:42:31,030 --> 00:42:32,000
are you covering it or not?

977
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:34,840
Say something now.

978
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:35,840
Yes or no?

979
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:39,800
I'll handle it, I definitely will.

980
00:42:40,800 --> 00:42:42,030
Uncle, just rest assured.

981
00:42:42,320 --> 00:42:43,630
I'll find a way to deal with this.

982
00:42:45,630 --> 00:42:46,480
I'm giving you three days.

983
00:42:47,670 --> 00:42:48,150
Three days.

984
00:42:48,550 --> 00:42:50,440
Get enough money
for your cousin's banquet,

985
00:42:50,670 --> 00:42:52,320
or don't bother about my life!

986
00:42:53,110 --> 00:42:54,800
Zhiyuan said he'll handle it, enough.

987
00:42:55,710 --> 00:42:56,150
Water.

988
00:42:57,030 --> 00:42:57,840
Slowly, don't choke.

989
00:42:58,000 --> 00:42:58,760
Slowly.

990
00:43:06,680 --> 00:43:08,560
♪If I close both eyes tonight♪

991
00:43:08,560 --> 00:43:12,440
♪Back to that wishing summer night♪

992
00:43:12,440 --> 00:43:16,200
♪Wind brushes your shaking frame♪

993
00:43:16,200 --> 00:43:21,000
♪That world feels close just the same♪

994
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:23,400
♪If I dare to face the dawn♪

995
00:43:23,400 --> 00:43:27,120
♪Do you know this face you'd drawn♪

996
00:43:27,120 --> 00:43:30,920
♪Gray spirals looped in endless chase♪

997
00:43:30,920 --> 00:43:35,720
♪Tracing tears not words they trace♪

998
00:43:35,720 --> 00:43:38,480
♪How many times must this repeat♪

999
00:43:38,480 --> 00:43:42,000
♪Sighs pull my gaze to retreat♪

1000
00:43:42,000 --> 00:43:45,840
♪Sleepless nights, risks untold♪

1001
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:50,640
♪None of it for my own soul♪

1002
00:43:50,640 --> 00:43:52,080
♪Winds blew, rains poured♪

1003
00:43:52,080 --> 00:43:53,960
♪Umbrellas broke, we soared♪

1004
00:43:53,960 --> 00:43:56,040
♪Sky fell, ground shook♪

1005
00:43:56,040 --> 00:43:57,560
♪Through dusk till dawn I stood♪

1006
00:43:57,560 --> 00:43:59,520
♪Cars passed, dreams drowned♪

1007
00:43:59,520 --> 00:44:04,920
♪Every stop's chain unbound♪

1008
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:06,960
♪Moon watched, stars blazed♪

1009
00:44:06,960 --> 00:44:08,840
♪Lamps died, connections phased♪

1010
00:44:08,840 --> 00:44:10,960
♪Held hands, laughed then cried♪

1011
00:44:10,960 --> 00:44:12,240
♪Hearts froze, parts died inside♪

1012
00:44:12,240 --> 00:44:14,880
♪Tried hard, spoke true♪

1013
00:44:14,880 --> 00:44:16,880
♪Now I'm someone I never knew♪

1014
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:21,880
♪Love came, hate stayed♪

1015
00:44:21,880 --> 00:44:23,400
♪I arrived, you frayed♪

1016
00:44:23,400 --> 00:44:24,760
♪Voice cracked, tears burned♪

1017
00:44:24,760 --> 00:44:26,760
♪Life lost, lessons earned♪

1018
00:44:27,120 --> 00:44:29,360
♪Grew up, let go♪

1019
00:44:29,360 --> 00:44:31,360
♪Why cling to old sorrow♪

1020
00:44:41,760 --> 00:44:44,720
♪How many loops replay♪

1021
00:44:44,720 --> 00:44:48,400
♪Sighs steal my gaze away♪

1022
00:44:48,400 --> 00:44:51,920
♪Lost nights, bold bets♪

1023
00:44:51,920 --> 00:44:56,560
♪Nothing for my regrets♪

1024
00:44:56,560 --> 00:45:00,960
♪Winds raged, storms crashed♪

1025
00:45:00,960 --> 00:45:03,640
♪Dawns broke, I held fast♪

1026
00:45:03,640 --> 00:45:05,760
♪Cars fled, dreams fled♪

1027
00:45:05,760 --> 00:45:11,240
♪Every route left dead♪

1028
00:45:11,240 --> 00:45:12,760
♪Love left, hate stayed♪

1029
00:45:12,760 --> 00:45:14,640
♪Voice gone, tears paid♪

1030
00:45:14,640 --> 00:45:18,280
♪Grew strong, moved on♪

1031
00:45:18,280 --> 00:45:20,280
♪Why dwell when it's gone♪
